text: The 2022–23 Austrian Cup is the 92nd edition of the national cup in Austrian football. Red Bull Salzburg are the defending champions. ==Round dates== The competition was held as follows. Round Match date Round 1 15-17 July 2022 Round 2 30 August - 1 September 2022 Round 3 18- 20 October 2022 Quarter- finals 3-5 February 2023 Semi-finals 4-5 April 2023 Final 30 April 2023 == First round == Thirty-two first round matches were played between 15 July and 17 July 2021. ==Second round== Sixteen second round matches were played between 30 August and 1 September 2022. ==Third round== Eight third round matches will be played between 18 and 20 October 2022. ==Quarter-finals== Four quarter-final matches will be played between 3 and 5 February 2023 ==Semi- finals== ==Final== SK Rapid Wien: Niklas Hedl – Jonas Auer, Martin Moormann, Kevin Wimmer, Thorsten Schick – Aleksa Pejić, Roman Kerschbaum – Marco Grüll (81.
